file.name: googleapis.com-storage-v1beta1-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  contact:
    name: Google
    url: https://google.com
  description: Lets you store and retrieve potentially-large, immutable data objects.
  license:
    name: Creative Commons Attribution 3.0
    url: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
  termsOfService: https://developers.google.com/terms/
  title: Cloud Storage
  version: v1beta1
  x-apiClientRegistration:
    url: https://console.developers.google.com
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - storage
  x-logo:
    url: https://cloud.google.com/storage/images/cloud-storage-logo.png
  x-origin:

        version: 2.7.31

      url: https://www.googleapis.com/discovery/v1/apis/storage/v1beta1/rest
      version: v1
  x-preferred: false
  x-providerName: googleapis.com
  x-serviceName: storage
externalDocs:
  url: https://developers.google.com/storage/docs/json_api/
tags:
  - name: bucketAccessControls
  - name: buckets
  - name: objectAccessControls
  - name: objects
paths:
  /b:
    get:
      description: Retrieves a list of buckets for a given project.
      operationId: storage.buckets.list
      parameters:
        - description: Maximum number of buckets to return.
          in: query
          name: max-results
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 0
        - description: A previously-returned page token representing part of the larger set
            of results to view.
          in: query
          name: pageToken
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: A valid API project identifier.
          in: query
          name: projectId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to no_acl.
          in: query
          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - full
              - no_acl
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Buckets"
      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_only
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_only
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
      tags:
        - buckets
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
    post:
      description: Creates a new bucket.
      operationId: storage.buckets.insert
      parameters:
        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to no_acl, unless the bucket
            resource specifies acl or defaultObjectAcl properties, when it
            defaults to full.
          in: query
          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - full
              - no_acl
      requestBody:
        $ref: "#/components/requestBodies/Bucket"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Bucket"
      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
      tags:

  "/b/{bucket}":
    delete:
      description: Deletes an empty bucket.
      operationId: storage.buckets.delete
      parameters:
        - description: Name of a bucket.
          in: path
          name: bucket
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":

      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:

    get:

      operationId: storage.buckets.get
      parameters:

          in: path
          name: bucket
          required: true
          schema:

        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to no_acl.

          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:

      responses:

          content:

      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_only
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_only
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
      tags:

    parameters:

      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"

          name: bucket
          required: true

            type: string
        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to full.
          in: query
          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:

              - no_acl
      requestBody:

      responses:

          content:
            "*/*":

                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Bucket"
      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
      tags:
        - buckets
    put:
      description: Updates a bucket.
      operationId: storage.buckets.update
      parameters:
        - description: Name of a bucket.
          in: path
          name: bucket
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to full.
          in: query
          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - full
              - no_acl
      requestBody:
        $ref: "#/components/requestBodies/Bucket"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Bucket"
      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.full_control
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
      tags:
        - buckets
  "/b/{bucket}/acl":

      description: Retrieves ACL entries on the specified bucket.
      operationId: storage.bucketAccessControls.list
      parameters:

          in: path

      responses:

      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"

          in: path
          name: bucket
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The entity holding the permission. Can be user-userId,

          in: path

      parameters:

        - description: The entity holding the permission. Can be user-userId,

  "/b/{bucket}/o":
    get:
      description: Retrieves a list of objects matching the criteria.
      operationId: storage.objects.list
      parameters:
        - description: Name of the bucket in which to look for objects.
          in: path
          name: bucket
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Returns results in a directory-like mode. items will contain only
            objects whose names, aside from the prefix, do not contain
            delimiter. Objects whose names, aside from the prefix, contain
            delimiter will have their name, truncated after the delimiter,
            returned in prefixes. Duplicate prefixes are omitted.
          in: query
          name: delimiter
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Maximum number of items plus prefixes to return. As duplicate
            prefixes are omitted, fewer total results may be returned than
            requested.
          in: query
          name: max-results
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 0
        - description: A previously-returned page token representing part of the larger set
            of results to view.
          in: query
          name: pageToken
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Filter results to objects whose names begin with this prefix.
          in: query
          name: prefix
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to no_acl.
          in: query
          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - full
              - no_acl

        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:

        - objects
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
    post:
      description: Stores new data blobs and associated metadata.
      operationId: storage.objects.insert
      parameters:
        - description: Name of the bucket in which to store the new object. Overrides the
            provided object metadata's bucket value, if any.
          in: path
          name: bucket
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Name of the object. Required when the object metadata is not
            otherwise provided. Overrides the object metadata's name value, if
            any.
          in: query
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to no_acl, unless the object
            resource specifies the acl property, when it defaults to full.
          in: query
          name: projection
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - full
              - no_acl
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/octet-stream:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Object"

          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/devstorage.read_write
      tags:

      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"

        - description: Set of properties to return. Defaults to full.

      requestBody:

      responses:

      security:
